              <div><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--verdigris, #4a7c59);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">WEB</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Seek Yahweh, all you humble of the land, who have kept his ordinances. Seek righteousness. Seek humility. It may be that you will be hidden in the day of Yahweh’s anger.</span></div>
