              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--ultramarine);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">YLT</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Ho! O inhabitants of the sea-coast, Nation of the Cherethites, A word of Jehovah [is] against you, Canaan, land of the Philistines, And I have destroyed thee without an inhabitant.</span></div>
              <div style="margin-bottom:0.6rem;"><span style="font-weight:700;color:var(--vermillion);font-size:0.8rem;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.05em;">ASV</span><br><span style="font-family:var(--font-reading);line-height:1.7;">Woe<S>1945</S> unto the inhabitants<S>3427</S> of the sea-coast<S>1471</S>, the nation of the Cherethites<S>3774</S>! The word<S>1697</S> of Jehovah<S>3068</S> is against you<S>3667</S>, O Canaan, the land<S>776</S> of the Philistines<S>6430</S>; I will destroy<S>6</S> thee<S>3427</S>, that there shall be no inhabitant.</span></div>
